  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "Mahatma Gandhi visited my high school with yoga training at Ranchi. He graciously wrote the above lines in the Ranchi guest-book. The translation is: \"This institution has deeply impressed my mind. I cherish high hopes that this school will encourage the further practical use of the spinning wheel.\""
  },
